#. Tag: author
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<personname><firstname>Ben</firstname><surname>Burton</surname></personname> "
"<email>bab@debian.org</email>"
msgstr ""
"<व्यक्तिनाम><प्रथमनाम>बेन्</firstname><surname>बर्टन</surname></personname> "
"<email>bab@debian.org</email>"

#. Tag: date
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "2003-04-07"
msgstr "२००३-०४-०७ ई"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reduce the number of #includes in &kde; source files"
msgstr "&kde इत्यत्र #includes इत्यस्य संख्यां न्यूनीकरोतु; स्रोतसञ्चिकाः"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> <group><option>-v, --verbose</option></group> "
"<group><option>-e, --experimental</option></group> <group><option>-m, --"
"modify</option></group> <group><option><replaceable>file</replaceable></"
"option></group> <group><option>--help</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes इति</command><group><option value=\"-v, --verbose\"> -"
"व, --वाच्य</option></group><group><option value=\"-e, --experimental\"> -ई, --"
"प्रयोगात्मकः</option></group><group><option value=\"-m, --modify\"> -म, --"
"संशोधय</option></group><group><option><replaceable> संचिका</replaceable></"
"option></group><group><option value=--help> --साहाय्यम्‌</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> tries to reduce the number of #includes in C+"
"+ source files. Much of it's processing is specific to &kde; sources and so "
"it might not work so well with sources for non-&kde; applications."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> C++ स्रोतसञ्चिकासु #includes इत्यस्य संख्यां न्यूनीकर्तुं "
"प्रयतते । तस्य प्रसंस्करणस्य अधिकांशं &kde; स्रोतः तथा च अ-&kde; अनुप्रयोगाः।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following problems are identified by <command>fixincludes</command>:"
msgstr "<command>fixincludes</command> इत्यनेन निम्नलिखितसमस्याः चिह्निताः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Including headers that are no longer supported but which exist for "
"compatibility with older Qt/KDE versions;"
msgstr ""
"शीर्षकं समाविष्टं ये अधुना समर्थिताः न सन्ति परन्तु ये प्राचीन Qt/KDE संस्करणैः सह संगततायै "
"विद्यन्ते;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Including the same file multiple times."
msgstr "एकमेव सञ्चिकां बहुवारं समाविष्टम्।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an experimental mode which tries removing each #include one at "
"a time (with a few exceptions) to see whether the source still compiles. "
"Note that this experimental mode will modify the original sources."
msgstr ""
"प्रयोगात्मकः मोडः अपि अस्ति यः प्रत्येकं #include एकैकं (कतिपय अपवादैः सह) निष्कासयितुं "
"प्रयतते यत् स्रोतः अद्यापि संकलनं करोति वा इति द्रष्टुं शक्नोति । ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् एषः "
"प्रयोगविधिः मूलस्रोतान् परिवर्तयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the sources will not be modified; the identified problems will "
"simply be written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण स्रोताः परिवर्तिताः न भविष्यन्ति; चिह्निताः समस्याः केवलं मानकनिर्गमं "
"प्रति लिखिताः भविष्यन्ति।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of C++ sources to examine should be given on the command-line. If "
"no files are given, all C++ sources in or beneath the current directory will "
"be examined (with the exception of directories whose <filename>Makefile.am</"
"filename> contains <option>-UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> or <option>-"
"UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option>)"
msgstr ""
"परीक्षणार्थं C++ स्रोतानां सूची आदेशपङ्क्तौ दातव्या । यदि सञ्चिकाः न दत्ताः तर्हि "
"वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायां वा अधः वा सर्वे C++ स्रोताः परीक्षिताः भविष्यन्ति (निर्देशिकाः "
"अपवादरूपेण येषां...<filename> मेकफाइल.अम्</filename> भरति<option value=-"
"UQT_NO_COMPAT> -UQT_NO_COMPAT</option> वा<option value=-UKDE_NO_COMPAT> -"
"UKDE_NO_COMPAT</option> )"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr "इयं उपयोगिता KDE Software Development Kit इत्यस्य भागः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --verbose"
msgstr "-व, --वाच्य"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Verbose mode. Additional debugging output is written to standard output."
msgstr "वर्बोज मोड। अतिरिक्तं त्रुटिनिवारणनिर्गमं मानकनिर्गमं प्रति लिख्यते ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "-e, --experimental"
msgstr "-ई, --प्रयोगात्मकः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Experimental mode, as described above in detail. Note that this option "
"implies <option>--modify</option>."
msgstr ""
"प्रयोगविधिः, यथा पूर्वं विस्तरेण वर्णितम् । ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् एषः विकल्पः "
"अभिप्रेतवान्<option value=--modify> --संशोधयतु</option> ."

#. Tag: option
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --modify"
msgstr "-म, --संशोधय"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as writing messages to standard output, actually modify the original "
"sources to fix any problems that were found."
msgstr ""
"मानकनिर्गमं प्रति सन्देशं लिखितुं च, वास्तवतः मूलस्रोतान् परिवर्तयन्तु यत् ये समस्याः प्राप्ताः "
"आसन् तान् निवारयितुं ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "लेखकाः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-fixincludes.1.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> was written by Dirk Mueller "
"<email>mueller@kde.org</email>."
msgstr ""
"<command>fixincludes</command> इति Dirk Mueller <email>mueller@kde.org</"
"email> इत्यनेन लिखितम् ।"
